about.summary: Rickshaw is an automated driver for Cyclus

name: rickshaw
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "rickshaw" %}
{% set version = "1.5.3" %}
{% set sha256 = "efe782cb7236ea58be5be895ae004940003dcd26fafdec759699b0b7e851100d" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - python-json-logger
    - pprintpp
    - jinja2

test:
  imports:
    - rickshaw

about:
  home: http://fuelcycle.org
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Rickshaw is an automated driver for Cyclus'
  dev_url: https://github.com/cyclus/rickshaw

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - scopatz
